description: I have NEW original, hard to find, Federal Pacific Electric ( FPE), also known as STAB-LOK, later also made by American Circuit Breaker and Challenger. I have more breakers of other sizes as well. I bought this equipment many years ago, before I retired and when Federal Pacific was Federal Pacific Electric and produced high grade equipment. FPE breakers later got a bad rap when after market breakers came in to the market.,Originally, Federal Pacific Electric ( FPE) was the only residential switching manufacturer using only copper, not aluminum, in their breakers and panels. This fact can be very important when installed near salt water, livestock or excessive moisture areas that can destroy aluminum.

title: Federal Pacific, ( FPE), stab-lok Circuit Breaker
description: I have NEW original, hard to find, Federal Pacific Electric ( FPE), also known as STAB-LOK, later also made by American Circuit Breaker and Challenger. These are NEW, original manufacturer, (OEM), breakers, not after market or refurbished (used and cleaned). I also have brand new original FPE sub panels and service panels of different types. I have more breakers of other sizes as well. I bought this equipment many years ago, before I retired and when Federal Pacific was Federal Pacific Electric and produced high grade equipment. FPE breakers later got a bad rap when after market breakers came in to the market.,Originally, Federal Pacific Electric ( FPE) was the only residential switching manufacturer using only copper, not aluminum, in their breakers and panels. This fact can be very important when installed near salt water, livestock or excessive moisture areas that can destroy aluminum.
